gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 126, Grizzlies 111
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Grizzlies, 126-111. Jamal Murray led Denver with 21 points, six rebounds, and four assists as Nikola Jokic added 15 points, 15 rebounds, and five assists. GG Jackson led the Grizzlies with a career-high 44 points, along with 12 rebounds. The Nuggets end the year at 57-25 as the Grizzlies end at 28-54.
